[I] 2D and 3D Graph Calculator

[T] KAlgebra is an application that can replace your graphing calculator. It
[T] has numerical, logical, symbolic, and analysis features that let you
[T] calculate mathematical expressions on the console and graphically plot the
[T] results in 2D or 3D.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kalgebra/

[A] The KDE-Team
